							<b><p> Goal Commitment</b><p>
								When you think about your commitment to your assigned goals for this global experience, would you <br>
							say you were <b><i>mostly independent</i></b> (i.e., you acted independently to revise your goals according to the <br>
							situation and/or your personal needs at the time) OR <b><i>mostly allegiant</i></b> (i.e., regardless of situational<br>
							pressures or your needs at the time, you remained totally committed to your original assigned goals)?<br>

